Package: libyaz++
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libyaz (>= 2.0.9)
Description: YAZ++ and ZOOM library.
 YAZ++ is a C++ library with an object oriented interface to YAZ and ZOOM.

